{"tid":2238388,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大家知唔知「政客」一詞係貶義","createTime":"2020-10-11T05:57:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T05:10:44.000Z","uid":288455,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cede11c0364547aec66ad9c6037d4cd0d1bdc6fa","tid":2238388,"uid":288455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T05:57:36.000Z","msg":"最近成日見到啲人亂用「政客」一詞，Trump 又叫政客，Biden 又叫政客，Pence 又叫政客，個個都叫政客，連區議員自己都稱自己做政客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。最誇張係頭先喺一個有關美國大選嘅post 入面，有個comment 話共和黨有一大班年輕有為嘅政客上緊位... 咁既然係年輕有為又點會係政客呢？<br />\n<br />\n其實「政客」一詞係貶義詞，形容一啲只為選票，隨波逐流，無貢獻嘅從政者，但又未至於去到「政棍」如建制派班垃圾咁樣。大家日後可以善用一啲中性詞，包括政要/政治家/政治人物/從政者等等，唔好再用「政客」一詞來形容自己支持嘅從政者，避免被人取笑"},{"pid":"ede32808819d6f83ab09715b78d611515b0d7443","tid":2238388,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T06:02:42.000Z","msg":"美國作家克拉克（James Freeman Clarke）如是說<br />\n而「政客」則是以政治為主副業，卻不嚴守職業道德的人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f857ff1e208f1e383430dba3f112ea946a0638c2","tid":2238388,"uid":248518,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T06:08:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ov3WWiB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fov3WWiB.png&h=1af9674d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n噉你可以提議一個更好嘅翻譯去提及politician嘅。"},{"pid":"0d155b23a82b183ece647566656da4cff98d9eed","tid":2238388,"uid":362827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T06:08:38.000Z","msg":"政治家囉，好偉大咁"},{"pid":"d10faf7775add96d95e286f676352eb6b2e8fbc2","tid":2238388,"uid":248518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f857ff1e208f1e383430dba3f112ea946a0638c2","tid":2238388,"uid":248518,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2